{
  "texts": [
    "Six radiology residents with less than 6 months of experience in neuroradiology were recruited from the local departments of radiology and neuroradiology as participants of the usability study and randomized into two groups.",
    "All participants provided informed consent.",
    "A total of twenty brain MRI exams obtained between 01/01/2016 and 12/31/2023 were selected from the local imaging database and randomized into two sets (Figure 1).",
    "In each brain MRI scan, the image finding in question was denoted by an arrow.",
    "Selection criteria for participants and MRI scans are shown in Table 1."
  ]
}